<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>There is a simple way to test if a weapon or anything<BR>
recharges over night in a bank slot (which it does NOT by<BR>
the way). Buy a Spring or Harvest Crystal off a vendor (5<BR>
charges of summon water/food) use a few and leave it in<BR>
your bank for a period of time. Nothing changes on the<BR>
amount of charges. Not ever!<BR>
<BR>
I thought the complete heal effect on the weapon could be<BR>
almost as good as Laying on Hands of a paladin. Then I<BR>
discovered that the weapon had a casting time and can be<BR>
interrupted as well... =P<BR>
<BR>
But a Shadowknight with a Scythe just looks extremely cool<BR>
IMNSHO.</font></td></tr></table>
